summary: This appears to be a header or metadata for an FBI 302 form (report of investigation) from the New York Field Office, Violent Crimes Task Force, concerning the Epstein case. It indicates the document was finalized and sent on September 18, 2019.
keyFacts: An FBI 302 report from the New York Field Office was finalized on September 18, 2019.
